  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO PROVIDE THAT THE FRIDAY BEFORE MEMORIAL DAY IS TO BE DESIGNATED ANNUALLY AS \"BUDDY POPPY DAY\" IN MISSISSIPPI IN HONOR OF THE OFFICIAL MEMORIAL FLOWER OF THE VETERANS OF FOREIGN WARS (VFW); AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
